data.description: Must see this wonderful Dayton Valley Home !  This well maintained and updated 3 bedroom, 2 bath with office/den is located in a quiet neighborhood close to schools, park, dinning & shopping. Walk into the huge newly remodeled gourmet kitchen that features tons of storage & counter space, an island, built in table and new appliances. New flooring throughout. Family room is open to the kitchen along with a separate dinning/playroom. Lots of natural lighting. All lighting in home is high-end stylish fixures. The Primary suite features newer double sinks & faucets, garden tub, separate shower stall and large walk-in closet. There is space for RV parking along with drive thru gate access on both sides of the house as well as a carport next th the garage. Finished deeper garage with large built-in workbench & shelving. 2 storage sheds, water softener & New water heater. Freshly painted inside & outside. The beautiful home is move in ready! SELLERS ARE EXTREMLY MOTIVATED AND OPEN TO A BUYER CREDIT.
